穿曬 <br />\n係陣容上鷹隊已經有足夠既準備去打殘猢人 <br />\n基本上直頭可以放nash狂射3分 <br />\n因為以teague依種體能怪物 <br />\n就算離進攻者10個身位 <br />\n都可以憑佢既活力同反應趕返去block柒 <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=lIxEpTPhM2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlIxEpTPhM2k&d=lHtYDDkazIyamgVJbGWsYW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b26ece04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=lIxEpTPhM2k</a> <br />\n<br />\n而係對付nash既p＆r，鷹隊根本未驚過 <br />\n就算gosol dh籃底攞到波都會比josh smith block柒,hill同jamison都唔例外 <br />\n<br />\n而blake不提也罷 <br />\nD防守仲差過我樓下8樓隻小學雞校隊 <br />\n出黎只會比teague侮辱 <br />\n而against熱水 <br />\n眾所周知,查馬is a shooter only <br />\nTeague can block him anytime <br />\n<br />\n至于Cole又未成氣候 <br />\n<br />\n所以pg位,鷹隊完勝"},{"pid":"b66e71ac7771022da2a9541c5233900e2cf33feb","tid":306220,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a11eeb9999156425a99df4a0864251a00cac30e","tid":306220,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來Facebook 有個咁既page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/193438_ce0a6e958e54c06ca26b8304696b4dc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F193438_ce0a6e958e54c06ca26b8304696b4dc9.jpg&h=48d201af&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abfe8967e260a82ca1fd58579411833c1fb9362","tid":306220,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"